title New Note Ajax Sequence

Browser->Server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note
note left of Browser: 
By submitting the html form element, 
the browser requests an http post to new_note,
sending the new note value
end note
Server-->Browser: 302 redirect status code to notes page
note right of Server: 
The server makes an http post request to new_note,
executing js-code which add the sent note to the existing notes array,
responding with a 302 status code 
and redirecting to notes page
end note
Browser->Server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/notes
Server-->Browser: HTML code
Browser->Server: HTTP GET https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/main.css
Server-->Browser: main.css
Browser->Server: https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/main.js
Server-->Browser: main.js
Browser->Server: https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/data.json
Server-->Browser: data.json
